#English helper

install_device=Download and start up the Brass Monkey application now. Make sure you device is on the same WiFi connection as your computer or smart tv.

see_device=Do you see your device listed in the box to the left? If so go to your device and select the option shown in the box.

try_device=Okay, Lets see if we can connect to your device on your WiFi network.

failed=Oops! Unfortunately, something about your network is preventing the connection. Check out our support page or contact us at <font color="#DA6323"><a href="mailto:support@playbrassmonkey.com">support@playbrassmonkey.com</a></font> for additional help.

success=Success! You are now ready to play games!

device_detected=Do you see your device listed in the box to the left? If so go to your device and select the option shown in the box.

no_device_detected=Make sure your mobile device is on the same WiFi network as your computer and that you have the Brass Monkey app opened.

select_device=Select your device type.

ios_instructions=<ol><li>Click on the "Settings" icon (with gears on it) on your iOS device</li><li>Select "WiFi"</li><li>Make sure that "Wi-Fi" is set to "on"</li><li>Choose the network from the list that shares a name with the network your computer is connected to</li><li>Click the "home" button (the button on your phone's face)</li><li>Locate and re-open the Brass Monkey app</li></ol>

android_instructions=<ol><li>Select "Settings"</li><li>Select "Wireless Networks"</li><li>Select "WiFi Settings"</li><li>Select the network from the list that shares a name with the network your computer is connected to</li><li>Return to your home screen and your apps</li><li>Locate and re-open the Brass Monkey app</li></ol>